<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 14:06:40 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>海法市试图阻止出版一本有关以色列-巴勒斯坦冲突的书</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/haifa-municipality-seeks-to-block-launch-of-a-book-on-the-israeli-palestinian-conflict/0000018d-78c8-d971-a38f-79fab7e30000</link><description>居民们对即将举行的活动表示反对，该活动计划推出该书的希伯来语译本，该书讲述了两个失去亲人的父亲（一个是以色列人，另一个是巴勒斯坦人）之间的友谊故事。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 13:41:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/haifa-municipality-seeks-to-block-launch-of-a-book-on-the-israeli-palestinian-conflict/0000018d-78c8-d971-a38f-79fab7e30000</guid></item><item><title>卡塔尔国家基金的以色列律师在人质谈判中为军队提供建议；以色列国防军：“不存在利益冲突”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-lawyer-to-qatari-state-fund-advises-idf-in-hostage-negotiations/0000018d-7929-d4f1-a18d-fd7954b70000</link><description>律师约瑟夫·本克尔代表卡塔尔慈善机构，这是卡塔尔政府控制的一个基金会，曾被用来向哈马斯转移资金。战争爆发后，本克尔被征召入以色列陆军预备役，担任人质谈判顾问</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 13:20:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-lawyer-to-qatari-state-fund-advises-idf-in-hostage-negotiations/0000018d-7929-d4f1-a18d-fd7954b70000</guid></item><item><title>在加沙，一名六岁儿童躺在坦克前的尸体中</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/in-gaza-a-6-year-old-lies-before-a-tank-among-the-bodies/0000018d-78b1-d4f1-a18d-fcf145400000</link><description>Hind Hamada 这个名字对以色列人来说没有任何意义。为什么会这样呢？但她的笑脸现在可能已为每个巴勒斯坦家庭所熟悉。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 13:08:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/in-gaza-a-6-year-old-lies-before-a-tank-among-the-bodies/0000018d-78b1-d4f1-a18d-fcf145400000</guid></item><item><title>美国是否终于揭穿了伊朗的虚张声势，对德黑兰支持的民兵进行了打击？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/is-the-u-s-finally-calling-irans-bluff-with-strikes-on-tehran-backed-militias/0000018d-78b1-dd6e-a98d-fcb3910c0000</link><description>美国最近对叙利亚、伊拉克和也门民兵组织的袭击没有具体的战略目标，也无意实现任何超出其目标的目标，但它们仍然可以重新洗牌伊朗认为自己完全控制的地区格局</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 13:03:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/is-the-u-s-finally-calling-irans-bluff-with-strikes-on-tehran-backed-militias/0000018d-78b1-dd6e-a98d-fcb3910c0000</guid></item><item><title>在主要捐助者因以色列指控而暂停援助后，西班牙将向近东救济工程处额外提供 380 万美元</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/spain-to-give-unrwa-extra-3-8-million-after-donors-suspend-aid-amid-israeli-allegations/0000018d-794d-d008-a9cd-fbfda3ce0000</link><description>邻国葡萄牙宣布向近东救济工程处提供价值100万欧元的额外援助。其外交部长写道，“在这个困难时刻，不要背弃巴勒斯坦人民”，这一点至关重要</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 13:01:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/spain-to-give-unrwa-extra-3-8-million-after-donors-suspend-aid-amid-israeli-allegations/0000018d-794d-d008-a9cd-fbfda3ce0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙战争打造了一部混乱的混搭音乐剧</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/the-war-in-gaza-has-created-a-chaotic-mash-up-musical/0000018d-74b8-d4f1-a18d-f4f8d56e0000</link><description>自战争开始以来，任何人都在发行歌曲，但一位从未录制过歌曲的艺术家伊丹·阿梅迪 (Idan Amedi) 成为了新闻头条。此外，一部有关六日战争的新音乐剧登陆以色列银幕</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 10:12:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/the-war-in-gaza-has-created-a-chaotic-mash-up-musical/0000018d-74b8-d4f1-a18d-f4f8d56e0000</guid></item><item><title>警方称，以色列人在贝尔谢巴袭击平民和警察后被枪杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-shot-dead-after-attacking-civilians-and-cops-in-beer-sheva-police-say/0000018d-788f-dd6e-a98d-fcaf727a0000</link><description>嫌疑人穆尔希德·阿卜杜勒·海伊写了一封遗书，然后离开了蒂拉的家。据警方称，他袭击了路人，高喊“真主至大”，随后警察开枪射中了他的腿部。他的兄弟否认警方的说法</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 10:03:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/israeli-shot-dead-after-attacking-civilians-and-cops-in-beer-sheva-police-say/0000018d-788f-dd6e-a98d-fcaf727a0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯在加沙北部重新崛起，以展示控制权</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/hamas-reemerges-in-northern-gaza-in-bid-to-demonstrate-control/0000018d-7857-d971-a38f-79f7ade40000</link><description>哈马斯正试图通过加强在北部地带和加沙城与以色列国防军的战斗以及展示对平民的控制来表明该组织仍然处于控制之中。到目前为止，大部分都是示范性的</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 09:36:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/hamas-reemerges-in-northern-gaza-in-bid-to-demonstrate-control/0000018d-7857-d971-a38f-79f7ade40000</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯召见以色列大使，指责克里姆林宫与哈马斯站在一起，淡化大屠杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/russia-to-summon-israeli-ambassador-over-unacceptable-comments/0000018d-7850-dd6e-a98d-fc720cd30000</link><description>在最近接受《生意人报》采访时，哈尔佩林严厉批评俄罗斯自10月7日袭击以来对哈马斯的立场，并指责俄罗斯外交部长谢尔盖·拉夫罗夫“淡化”大屠杀</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 08:13:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/russia-to-summon-israeli-ambassador-over-unacceptable-comments/0000018d-7850-dd6e-a98d-fc720cd30000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯报告称，加沙隔夜袭击造成 100 多人死亡，以色列等待人质协议回应</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article-live/israel-awaits-hamas-response-defense-chief-to-biden-envoy-open-to-diplomacy-with-lebanon/0000018d-775c-dd6e-a98d-f77eab370000</link><description>火箭弹瞄准以色列北部和南部 ■ 阿拉伯裔以色列男子在以色列南部试图从警察身上夺取武器后被枪杀 ■ 以色列国防部长告诉拜登特使，以色列愿意通过外交解决黎巴嫩冲突，但为其他情况做好准备 ■ 卡塔尔消息人士：美国试图让哈马斯相信，暂停后恢复战斗对以色列来说将是困难的</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 04:32:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article-live/israel-awaits-hamas-response-defense-chief-to-biden-envoy-open-to-diplomacy-with-lebanon/0000018d-775c-dd6e-a98d-f77eab370000</guid></item><item><title>本-格维尔对《华尔街日报》的攻击不是针对白宫，而是针对内塔尼亚胡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/netnayahu-again-lets-ben-gvir-make-a-weakling-out-of-him/0000018d-75b9-dd6e-a98d-f5bb786d0000</link><description>乔·拜登并不真正关心这位极右翼以色列部长何时希望特朗普回归，并指责他的政府更愿意支持哈马斯而不是帮助以色列。但内塔尼亚胡将不得不应对这一反弹</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 01:17:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/netnayahu-again-lets-ben-gvir-make-a-weakling-out-of-him/0000018d-75b9-dd6e-a98d-f5bb786d0000</guid></item><item><title>美国对以色列的紧急援助正处于十字路口，参众两院公布了对决措施</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/house-gop-standalone-bill-on-emergency-israel-aid-faces-deep-internal-opposition/0000018d-7644-d971-a38f-77f61d060000</link><description>美国总统乔·拜登表示，参议院法案“为以色列提供了他们所需要的”。如果该法案未能通过，国会面临的压力只会越来越大，要求考虑通过独立于乌克兰、台湾和边境安全措施的以色列援助</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Feb 2024 23:07:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/house-gop-standalone-bill-on-emergency-israel-aid-faces-deep-internal-opposition/0000018d-7644-d971-a38f-77f61d060000</guid></item><item><title>消息来源：哈马斯正在考虑达成协议，而其武装分子则试图在以色列清理的地区重新集结</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/sources-hamas-mulls-deal-while-its-militants-try-to-regroup-in-areas-israel-says-cleared/0000018d-75df-d971-a38f-75ff2d180000</link><description>随着停火协议正在谈判中，哈马斯希望表明，即使经过四个月的战斗，它仍然保留了行动和组织能力</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Feb 2024 22:17:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-05/ty-article/.premium/sources-hamas-mulls-deal-while-its-militants-try-to-regroup-in-areas-israel-says-cleared/0000018d-75df-d971-a38f-75ff2d180000</guid></item><item><title>以色列高等法院断然驳回宣布总理内塔尼亚胡不适合任职的上诉</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-high-court-flatly-rejects-appeal-to-declare-pm-netanyahu-unfit-for-office/0000018d-7596-d4f1-a18d-f5f611840000</link><description>法官们表示，请愿者，其中包括前国防部长摩西·亚阿隆、前参谋长丹·哈鲁茨和纳马·拉齐米，没有给总理足够的时间做出回应，并包含了法院已经听取的论点</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Feb 2024 20:34:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-high-court-flatly-rejects-appeal-to-declare-pm-netanyahu-unfit-for-office/0000018d-7596-d4f1-a18d-f5f611840000</guid></item><item><title>“与哈马斯勾结的叛徒”：内塔尼亚胡支持针对对手的恶意指控</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-02-04/ty-article/.highlight/traitors-in-cahoots-with-hamas-netanyahu-backs-poisonous-claims-against-opponents/0000018d-7515-d971-a38f-75b74dc90000</link><description>自战争开始以来，毒药就在网上传播，阴谋论指责内塔尼亚胡的反对者造成了死亡和破坏。反改革抗议运动的领导人希克马·布雷斯勒 (Shikma Bressler) 并没有平静地对待这些袭击</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Feb 2024 19:51:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-02-04/ty-article/.highlight/traitors-in-cahoots-with-hamas-netanyahu-backs-poisonous-claims-against-opponents/0000018d-7515-d971-a38f-75b74dc90000</guid></item><item><title>以色列银行冻结了美国第一轮制裁目标的以色列定居者的账户</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-bank-blocks-account-of-israeli-settler-targeted-by-first-round-of-u-s-sanctions/0000018d-7532-d4f1-a18d-f5724bac0000</link><description>以色列国民银行是第一家针对美国总统乔·拜登决定对四名以色列定居者实施制裁而采取行动的以色列银行。预计其他银行也将采取类似措施，以避免在美国产生法律影响。</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Feb 2024 19:04:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-bank-blocks-account-of-israeli-settler-targeted-by-first-round-of-u-s-sanctions/0000018d-7532-d4f1-a18d-f5724bac0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列内阁同意延长有争议的公民法</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-cabinet-okays-extension-of-controversial-citizenship-law/0000018d-7541-dd6e-a98d-f563c9fa0000</link><description>该法律最初于 2002 年第二次起义期间通过，该法律禁止巴勒斯坦人与以色列居民结婚而获得以色列居民身份，此后每年都延长该法律</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Feb 2024 18:20:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-cabinet-okays-extension-of-controversial-citizenship-law/0000018d-7541-dd6e-a98d-f563c9fa0000</guid></item><item><title>随着哈马斯协议的临近，以色列卫生部修改了照顾被释放人质的政策</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-04/ty-article/.premium/as-hamas-deal-looms-israels-health-ministry-revises-policy-for-care-of-released-hostages/0000018d-7482-d4f1-a18d-f4f230b90000</link><description>新指令基于 11 月底第一批人质在加沙地带获释后吸取的经验教训</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Feb 2024 17:05:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-04/ty-article/.premium/as-hamas-deal-looms-israels-health-ministry-revises-policy-for-care-of-released-hostages/0000018d-7482-d4f1-a18d-f4f230b90000</guid></item><item><title>达西·埃利希 (Dassi Erlich) 打倒了施虐者马尔卡·莱弗 (Malka Leifer)。现在她讲述了她的完整故事</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2024-02-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/dassi-erlich-took-her-abuser-malka-leifer-down-now-she-tells-her-full-story/0000018d-6518-d32e-a3cf-efd8af470000</link><description>达西·埃利希 (Dassi Erlich) 的新回忆录《恶意》(In Bad Faith) 全面展现了现年 36 岁的她作为母亲、姐妹、妻子和女儿、虐待家庭的受害者、操纵性的校长和冷酷的极端正统犹太社区的形象。</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Feb 2024 16:04:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2024-02-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/dassi-erlich-took-her-abuser-malka-leifer-down-now-she-tells-her-full-story/0000018d-6518-d32e-a3cf-efd8af470000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人在玩枪时意外杀死朋友后被控鲁莽杀人罪</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-charged-with-reckless-homicide-after-killing-friend-while-toying-with-gun/0000018d-7486-d971-a38f-75b6da060000</link><description>根据起诉书，23 岁的阿维亚·阿巴约夫 (Aviya Abayof) 来自约旦河西岸定居点 Ma&amp;#39;aleh Adumim，当时他正在玩朋友的枪械，无意中射杀了另一位朋友。在国家安全部长本-格维尔加快授权程序后，枪支拥有者获得了执照</description><pubDate>Sun, 04 Feb 2024 16:01:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-charged-with-reckless-homicide-after-killing-friend-while-toying-with-gun/0000018d-7486-d971-a38f-75b6da060000</guid></item></channel></rss>